It's already clear where the problems lie. It will probably be VERY difficult to get medical clearance, due to the FAA's opinion on certain medications.
It's not impossible, but it will take a VERY long time and means a LOT of extra work.
That's admittedly somewhat discouraging, but nonetheless just another problem that one has to solve. So far, it seems to be solvable. It just costs a lot of time and money.
